	- Rotation (to right)       MENU("Rotation")
	- Rotation (to left)        IF(FIRSTSEL|(CURSMODE(-2)<2),MENU("Rotat"):MENU("Rotat"):MENU("Rotat"),0)
    Third line :
	- Orthogonal mode ON/OFF    SETORTHO(-1)
		Initialization	    SETORTHO(-2)==0
	- Use grid ON/OFF	    SNAPGRID(-1)
		Initialieation	    SNAPGRID(-2)==0
	- Place output connector    UNMARK(-1):MENU("Place output")
	- Place GROUND2 	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Masse2",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place GROUND		    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Masse",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Symmetry		    MENU("Reflection")
	- Pull wires ON/OFF	    MENU("Pull lines")
    Fourth line :
	- Draw double lines	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(2):DRAWMODE(2)
		Initialization	    (CURSMODE(-2)==2)&(DRAWMODE(1000)==2)
	- Place boxes		    UNMARK(-1):DRAWMODE(1):CURSMODE(22)
		Initialization	    CURSMODE(-1)==22
	- Place powers		    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Alimentation",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place PNP transistors     UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Transistor PNP",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place NPN transistors     UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Transistor NPN",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Add reference & value     CALL("EditString")
	- Clone objects 	    MENU("Clone")
    Fifth line :
	- Draw dashed lines	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(2):DRAWMODE(0)
		Initialisation	    (CURSMODE(-2)==2)&(DRAWMODE(1000)==0)
	- Place triangles	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(26)
		Initialisation	    CURSMODE(-2)==26
	- Surface		    CURSMODE(-1):SETFILL(IF(SETFILL(-1),0,1))
		Initialisation	    SETFILL(-1)
	- Place DELs		    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Diode électroluminescente",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place sources 	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Générateur",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Fix on grid		    MENU("Fix on grid")
	- Divide size		    MENU("Divide size")
    Sixth line :
	- Place special line	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(2):DRAWMODE(-1)
		Initialisation	    (CURSMODE(-2)==2)&(DRAWMODE(1000)<0)
	- Place ellipse/cercle	    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(10)
		Initialisation	    CURSMODE(-1)==10
	- Add references	    CALL("Référencer")
	- Place diodes		    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Diode",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place zeners		    UNMARK(-1):CURSMODE(-1):PUTPART("Diode Zener",-1,-1):CURSMODE(1):DRAWMODE(1)
	- Place to back 	    MENU("To Back")
