  @{"FONTNAME" LINK FONTNAME} name of character font to use
  @{"FONTSIZE" LINK FONTSIZE} size of character font to use
  @{"FOR     " LINK FOR} processing of a loop
  @{"GETARRAY" LINK GETARRAY} returns the value of an array object
  @{"GETCOLOR" LINK GETCOLOR} returns the RGB levels of a given colour
  @{"GETDEVS " LINK GETDEVS } number of gates in a circuit
  @{"GETLABEL" LINK GETLABEL} read the label number of a line
  @{"GETLINE " LINK GETLINE} get a line
  @{"GETMASK " LINK GETMASK} read the PCB mask of a component
  @{"GETMODEL" LINK GETMODEL} read the simulation model
  @{"GETNET  " LINK GETNET} read the line number associated with a label
  @{"GETNODES" LINK GETNODES} read the nodes list associated to a component
  @{"GETPOINT" LINK GETPOINT} get a point
