  @{"GETREF  " LINK GETREF } read the reference of a component
  @{"GETVAL  " LINK GETVAL } read the value or some type of component
  @{"GROUP   " LINK GROUP } creates a new group
  @{"GETZONE " LINK GETZONE} get a box
  @{"HEIGHT  " LINK HEIGHT } return the width of a object
  @{"HELP    " LINK HELP } display an AmigaGuide help
  @{"HSCALE  " LINK HSCALE } return the horizontal scale value of an object
  @{"IF      " LINK IF } test
  @{"INIT    " LINK INIT } initialization of variable
  @{"INPUT   " LINK INPUT } place an input connector
  @{"JUNCTION" LINK JUNCTION } place a connection
  @{"LANGUAGE" LINK LANGUAGE} name of the locale
  @{"LEN     " LINK LEN} length of the character string
  @{"LIBRARY " LINK LIBRARY} return the name of a component library
  @{"LIBSPATH" LINK LIBSPATH} specify drawer containing the symbol libraries
  @{"LINE    " LINK LINE} number of the line where to locate a object
  @{"LINKLAB " LINK LINKLAB} links a label to a line
  @{"LINKREF " LINK LINKREF} assignment of a reference with a component
  @{"LINKVAL " LINK LINKVAL} assignment of a value with a component
  @{"LOAD    " LINK LOAD} loading of a diagram
  @{"LOADBAR " LINK LOADBAR} load a toolbar
  @{"LOADCLIP" LINK LOADCLIP} load a clip
  @{"LOADLIB " LINK LOADLIB} load a symbol library
  @{"LOADPAGE" LINK LOADPAGE} load a page
  @{"LOCK    " LINK LOCK} lock user input
  @{"MAP     " LINK MAP} program a keyboard sequence
